page.title: 02Shenfield Station
page.content: Shenfield Station is one of the biggest buildings in Shenfield.There are several facilities for the public: phone boxes - three outside and one inside-, a photo booth and a paper stall.There are two ticket windows, five platforms, one buffet and 3 waiting rooms for five lines. This town being no more than half an hour away from London a lot of commuters live in Hutton and Shenfield. It is a vital station for commuters going to London and other major towns. This has made Hutton a popular place to live so rates and the cost of houses are high. Freightliner trains also pass through Shenfield.
